{"tid":983130,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"理性會唔會影響關係","createTime":"2019-01-15T16:53:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T15:28:35.000Z","uid":50980,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c8b24b9f604460b99d3b627068935d5b4d7364be","tid":983130,"uid":50980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T16:53:07.000Z","msg":"我自己比較理性  會分析女朋友的訴苦同埋有咩解決方案   仲會比較諗同佢有無將來  <br />\n但係女友比較感性 好隨性而行 做野無咩計劃  有時工作多仲會喊<br />\n有咩方法可以救下段關係？  我仲係鍾意佢  不過成日下意識會分析佢講的故事  覺得唔係企係佢個邊    我可以點改變自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b59a241948870fd5b13a04a1b2d56265c6940a4","tid":983130,"uid":29929,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T16:54:34.000Z","msg":"同女人分析都on撚9<br />\n佢唔係要你分析 你估佢唔知自己有時錯咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a17341bc01a26a486c2b969ddc0e03ca32434f7","tid":983130,"uid":227048,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T07:11:06.000Z","msg":"大家互補不足，唔好咩？<br />\ngood match <br />\n你女朋友只係想你聽下佢講野...<br />\n不用太認真去分析"},{"pid":"d11d9b04e3fcea118cb617fac4dbf9770986d13f","tid":983130,"uid":50980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a17341bc01a26a486c2b969ddc0e03ca32434f7","tid":983130,"uid":227048,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T07:11:06.000Z","msg":"大家互補不足，唔好咩？<br />\ngood match <br />\n你女朋友只係想你聽下佢講野...<br />\n不用太認真去分析"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T13:26:24.000Z","msg":"我都開始反省自己係咪應該咩都附和  企埋係佢個邊一齊屌......唔好分析咁多..............就算有無理由發嬲都唔同佢講道理....只係驚自己條氣唔順, 又打返原型........"},{"pid":"1427c1a6318dcda8188d6e96b2383ce463b20770","tid":983130,"uid":153827,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T13:31:26.000Z","msg":"你同女人講理性？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n算啦，你返屋企打飛機算啦，唔好害人啦...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fb71a0